credit.credit-words: The Book of Psalms for Singing
Be ready with Thy hand to help, Because Thy precepts are my choice.
I’ve longed for Thy salvation, L
, And in Thy holy law rejoice.
Oh, let Thine ordinances help; My soul shall live and praise Thee yet.
A straying sheep, Thy servant, seek, For Thy commands I ne’er forget.
